General Assembly Of North Carolina Session 2025
1 ANNUAL REPORTING
2 SECTION 7.1. Annually by February 1, beginning February 1, 2027, the Department
3 of Health and Human Services shall compile an annual Midlife Health Report identifying gaps
4 in health insurance coverage for essential midlife healthcare services and evaluating healthcare
5 disparities among midlife women residing in the State. The report shall be submitted to the Joint
6 Legislative Oversight Committee on Health and Human Services and the Fiscal Research
7 Division and made publicly available on the Department's website.
